<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你们会自己做午餐吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦、波比、贾森、莉琪和尼娜坐在地毯上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天他们又来到了儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜开口了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会，但是我妈妈希望我会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天你们要自己做三明治。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以明天带到学校作午餐。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的父母很忙，这样他们一定会很开心！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有金枪鱼沙拉和鸡蛋沙拉三明治的食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>选一种你想做的三明治。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜和伊坦选金枪鱼沙拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森、波比和莉琪选鸡蛋沙拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鸡蛋沙拉组，现在要煮鸡蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把鸡蛋放进一锅水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我来打开炉子。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们边等边混合蛋黄酱吧。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好不好？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好主意。” 波比点点头，拿起蛋黄酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把蛋黄酱和芥末酱混合起来。” 贾森念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些是切好的黄瓜。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“金枪鱼沙拉组，” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要打开罐头。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦拿起开罐器，放在罐头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>转呀、转呀、转呀。他打开了罐头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是怎么做到的？” 尼娜问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我转了把手，但是不行！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能是刀片没有切到金属。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要这样紧紧抓住把手。” 伊坦做给她看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 尼娜笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们沥干金枪鱼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把蛋黄酱与盐和黄瓜混合起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鸡蛋好了！可以剥皮切碎了。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师点点头。“你们剥皮，我来切。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我们来切。” 贾森拿起刀说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们本来就应该自己做这份午餐。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心点，贾森。” 雪莉老师提醒他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着他切鸡蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有的时候，获得一点帮助也没关系。” 她补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做鸡蛋沙拉的孩子们把鸡蛋和蛋黄酱混合起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做金枪鱼沙拉的孩子们把金枪鱼和蛋黄酱混合起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们准备好做三明治了！” 孩子们同时说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 雪莉老师哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小厨师们真棒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把沙拉涂在面包上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把另外一片面包放在上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们要把三明治包起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们明天可以带去作午餐！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把纸分给大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一种特别的纸。它会帮三明治保鲜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们用纸包住三明治。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，贾森包得不太顺利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我包不好！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮你吗，贾森？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以把三明治放在纸的正中间。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要回家了，贾森跑到妈妈身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我做了明天的午餐。全是我自己做的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师帮了我。” 他补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有时候，获得一点帮助也没关系。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>